WEBVTT

00:00.029 --> 00:01.276
Surprise!

00:01.870 --> 00:05.110
And my current husband is being
told he's going to be losing his job.

00:05.110 --> 00:07.310
What's happening to you?!
You're acting mental!

00:07.310 --> 00:10.230
You sound so surprised.

00:10.830 --> 00:12.430
You are good enough.

00:12.430 --> 00:13.910
You can do it.

00:13.910 --> 00:15.550
But you have to take your chance.

00:15.550 --> 00:17.710
Promise me you won't hurt yourself again.

00:17.710 --> 00:19.110
I promise.

00:19.110 --> 00:21.270
I just want to talk, if you'll let me.

00:21.270 --> 00:23.830
No, no! No, Finn, move out of the...

00:23.830 --> 00:27.590
Right.

00:27.590 --> 00:29.870
Kester Gill doesn't work here any more.

00:29.870 --> 00:31.390
He hasn't worked here since April.

00:31.390 --> 00:35.390
Why are you doing this?!

00:39.550 --> 00:40.990
You have until five.

00:40.990 --> 00:44.990
