00:48.750 --> 00:52.030
RAE: I need to come back.
I wanna move back in.

00:52.030 --> 00:53.830
- DR ALLEN: I disagree.
- And I want the pills.

00:53.830 --> 00:54.950
The ones I had last time.

00:54.950 --> 00:57.830
- I won't recommend those.
- Well, they'll be in the file.

00:57.830 --> 01:01.830
No, I'm sorry. Not unless
I deem them necessary.

01:01.990 --> 01:03.710
I rang Dr Gill.

01:03.710 --> 01:05.390
Told him you'd come in.

01:05.390 --> 01:07.270
He said there was no need.

01:07.270 --> 01:09.550
- No need?
- For you to be here.

01:09.550 --> 01:11.110
What else did he say?

01:11.110 --> 01:14.550
He said that you'd been working your
way through your final few sessions

01:14.550 --> 01:17.910
but that, in his view, you
were ready to finish therapy.

01:17.910 --> 01:19.630
That's it, is it?

01:19.630 --> 01:23.630
