person I care about the most.

04:41.870 --> 04:44.550
But by that point, it didn't
matter, Rae, because we did it.

04:44.550 --> 04:47.310
You'd got there.

04:47.310 --> 04:49.230
You were ready.

04:49.230 --> 04:52.630
Yeah, and then all the bad
stuff started happening.

04:52.630 --> 04:54.990
Because of the work you did,

04:54.990 --> 04:58.830
