09:43.790 --> 09:45.470
Whoa, Rae, what's going on?

09:45.470 --> 09:47.070
Nothing.

09:47.070 --> 09:50.670
Well, it doesn't look like nothing.

09:50.670 --> 09:54.670
- I just came to pick Rae up.
- It's fine.

09:56.590 --> 09:59.150
Rae, is there something
you're not telling me?

09:59.150 --> 10:00.670
No.

10:00.670 --> 10:04.190
Hiya, Katie, you OK?

10:04.190 --> 10:06.990
Just so you know, if I found out
you've done something to my mate cry

10:06.990 --> 10:09.070
while I've been in hospital,

10:09.070 --> 10:11.550
I'm gonna do something to make you cry.

10:11.550 --> 10:13.950
D'you know what I'm saying?

10:13.950 --> 10:16.990
Yeah.

10:16.990 --> 10:19.990
- Right, I'll call you later.
- OK.

10:19.990 --> 10:23.990
Come on.

10:26.830 --> 10:28.430
ENGINE STARTS

10:28.430 --> 10:32.430
